<h2 class="bold font-l">Drago Bludvist [Evil]</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Drago Bludvist, the General of the Dragon Army, uses intimidation to frighten individual dragons in a &quot;beat the dog until it stops barking&quot; sort of way and even tortured a Bewilderbeast after it first hatched so that he could have an alpha to mind-control all other dragons </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GoodTamingEvilTaming" class='trope-example-link'>Good Taming, Evil Taming</a></p>
